### Cart API Examples
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@anonymousToken = {{$guid}}
@userId = your-user-id-here

### ========================================
### ANONYMOUS USER EXAMPLES
### ========================================

### Get anonymous cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}

### Add part to anonymous cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/part?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partId": "part-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 1,
  "customizationOptions": {
    "selectedColor": "red",
    "selectedSize": "large"
  }
}

### Add sticker to anonymous cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/sticker?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stickerId": "sticker-uuid-here",
  "width": 100,
  "height": 50,
  "vinyl": true,
  "printed": false,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Add powdercoat service to anonymous cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/powdercoat-service?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "powdercoatingServiceId": "service-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 1,
  "color": "Matte Black"
}

### Update part quantity in anonymous cart
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/part/amount/part-order-item-id?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 3
}

### Remove part from anonymous cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/part/part-order-item-id?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}

### Clear anonymous cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/clear?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}

### Delete anonymous cart completely
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart?anonymousToken={{anonymousToken}}

### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATED USER EXAMPLES
### ========================================

### Get authenticated user's cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart?userId={{userId}}

### Add part to authenticated user's cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/part?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partId": "part-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 1,
  "customizationOptions": {
    "selectedColor": "blue",
    "selectedSize": "medium"
  }
}

### Add sticker to authenticated user's cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/sticker?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stickerId": "sticker-uuid-here",
  "width": 150,
  "height": 75,
  "vinyl": false,
  "printed": true,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Add powdercoat service to authenticated user's cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/powdercoat-service?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "powdercoatingServiceId": "service-uuid-here",
  "quantity": 1,
  "color": "Glossy Red"
}

### Update sticker quantity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/sticker/amount/order-item-id?userId={{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5
}

### Remove sticker from cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/sticker/order-item-id?userId={{userId}}

### Clear authenticated user's cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/clear?userId={{userId}}

### ========================================
### UTILITY ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### Get recommendations to reach 100 CHF
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "costAmount": 75.50,
  "itemsIdInCart": ["item-id-1", "item-id-2"]
}

### Manual cleanup of expired anonymous carts (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/scheduler/cart-cleanup/manual

### ========================================
### NOTES
### ========================================
# - Replace {{anonymousToken}} with a real UUID for testing
# - Replace {{userId}} with actual user ID
# - Replace UUIDs in bodies with actual IDs from your database
# - Anonymous carts expire after 72 hours
# - All cart endpoints accept either userId OR anonymousToken
# - Cannot use both userId and anonymousToken in same request
